{"tid":2356840,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"梁芷珊稱被恒生取消銀行戶口 暫未知原因","createTime":"2021-01-07T04:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T12:10:22.000Z","uid":240362,"like":305,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"5de9f2d037228c4467bb22adafc9d2e3364bc45e","tid":2356840,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T04:53:04.000Z","msg":"芷珊今日在其個人社交平台透露，其恒生銀行的兩個公司商業戶口，被通知一個月內停止運作，暫時原因未明。<br />\n<br />\n根據恒生的通知信件指，暫停戶口的原因可因為客戶盡職調查未獲通過、可疑交易等，為避免潛在欺詐或金融罪行，基於這些原因，銀行會中止部份客戶戶口。<br />\n<br />\n梁芷珊在社交平台指，兩個戶口每日都有往來入帳與支出，從來沒有負數、借貸或欠銀行錢。她狠批恒生猶如「中資銀行」，香港的銀行竟然連香港人都不服務，「而家銀行唔係銀行，家不是家。香港仲做咩國際商業城市？」<br />\n<br />\n她更以「國際ATM card」比喻為香港，「巨人千瘡百孔，口袋𥚃唯一work嘅國際ATM card，你走去整花佢條磁帶，搞佢個chip，仲可以繼續利用佢？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210107/OMMRHO7FAFDOHF6CANFXZWUGZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210107%2FOMMRHO7FAFDOHF6CANFXZWUGZU%2F&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5vaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=3120f59e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210107%2FOMMRHO7FAFDOHF6CANFXZWUGZU%2F&h=dcfc69ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210107/OMMRHO7FAFDOHF6CANFXZWUGZU/</a>"},{"pid":"4d2ed818894fd1921a792558442c29a755ac1248","tid":2356840,"uid":53498,"like":142,"dislike":2,"score":140,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T04:54:55.000Z","msg":"匯豐銀行全力奶共"},{"pid":"18feec9a1cb5104bc90225bd50ed5c47936568a3","tid":2356840,"uid":50615,"like":100,"dislike":2,"score":98,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T04:55:15.000Z","msg":"咁我都取消恒生戶口啦🏳️"},{"pid":"5b434abc8157a38103bf66fb83dd848025e3b15f","tid":2356840,"uid":51271,"like":67,"dislike":2,"score":65,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T04:56:08.000Z","msg":"恆心終於變支資"},{"pid":"7fe9d3260e7f9e0b18a8f70af14f213073b7b62f","tid":2356840,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T04:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kil